Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TOSHI, are you ready？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁是are you ready啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.14,0:02:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对那群食人鱼你叫我怎么let's party啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今  我们只能一起上了
